metadata.author: Momma Bear Audio
metadata.description:
Join host Ms. Rylee as she takes listeners through an educational and laughter-filled journey all about farts! Kids will discover the science behind these natural bodily functions, learn about farting animals, and explore the connection between food and flatulence. Combining curiosity, humor, and a healthy dose of toots, this audio series is an entertaining way to spark laughter and learning.

The fart segments include:
-Fart Facts: Discover fascinating facts about farts
-Famous Farters: Historical figures known for their legendary toots
-Farting Animals: Funny farting animals
-Fart Jokes: Hilarious jokes all about farts
-Fart Superpowers: Pick your favorite fart powered superhero
-Fart Games: The fart version of would you rather
-Fart Sounds: Giggle along with a variety of funny toot noises
